data.description: Embark on a journey through this impressive 2-story home situated in the sought-after North Point community! This spacious residence features 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a 2-car garage, and the exciting potential for even more space with its unfinished basement. Discover a wealth of desirable features, including granite countertops, premium cabinets, a tankless water heater for on-demand hot water, efficient A/C for optimal climate control, stylish laminate plank floors that add a touch of elegance, and an energy-efficient furnace. Step into the fully fenced backyard, providing both privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities. The primary bedroom comes with a delightful deck, offering a private retreat. Notably, the home boasts solar panels, contributing to lower utility bills. For your peace of mind, a First American 1-year Home Warranty is included. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this impressive home in the North Point community yours. Schedule a visit today and explore the potential and comfort it has to offer!
